  "slug": "oat-flapjacks",
  "title": "Oat flapjacks",
  "subtitle": "Golden syrup oat bars, chewy or crisp depending on how long they bake",
  "excerpt": "Sixteen flapjacks from a 20 x 20 cm tin: rolled oats bound with butter, golden syrup, and muscovado sugar, pressed into the tin and baked until golden at the edges. Short baking gives chewy bars; an extra 5 minutes gives a crisper snap. Score while warm, cool completely before cutting.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "Mrs Beeton, Book of Household Management (1861), Project Gutenberg #10136: the oaten biscuit section documents a baked oat mixture bound with butter and treacle or syrup, pressed into a tin and cut after baking. Eliza Acton, Modern Cookery for Private Families (1845), Project Gutenberg: the oat cake chapter documents the use of golden syrup as a binding agent in baked oat mixtures. The British flapjack in its standard form of rolled oats, butter, sugar, and golden syrup is documented across domestic baking literature from the late Victorian period onward.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Flapjacks have four ingredients and take 10 minutes to put together. The one decision is texture: bake for 20 minutes and the bars are chewy; bake for 25 and they are crispier and snap more cleanly. Either way, "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "score them while warm",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmp8793360000bkv4k6tc82b0"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ": flapjacks crack if you try to cut them cold."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What you need"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ingredientsList",
        "attrs": {
          "items": [
            {
              "name": "Unsalted butter",
              "unit": "g",
              "amount": 175,
              "prepNote": null,
              "groupLabel": null,
              "isOptional": false,
              "ingredientId": "cmp49f3gf000wrkv4p017cubd",
              "ingredientSlug": "unsalted-butter"
            },
            {
              "name": "Light muscovado sugar",
              "unit": "g",
              "amount": 125,
              "prepNote": null,
              "groupLabel": null,
              "isOptional": false,
              "ingredientId": "cmp871t3m000i2wv4o4v93oj3",
              "ingredientSlug": "light-muscovado-sugar"
            },
            {
              "name": "Golden syrup",
              "unit": "g",
              "amount": 75,
              "prepNote": null,
              "groupLabel": null,
              "isOptional": false,
              "ingredientId": "cmp49faxw00e1rkv49ri4h15s",
              "ingredientSlug": "golden-syrup"
            },
            {
              "name": "Fine sea salt",
              "unit": "g",
              "amount": 3,
